{"blogid": "123913216", "writerAge": "码龄5年", "writerBlogNum": "57", "writerCollect": "27", "writerComment": "2", "writerFan": "96", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "670", "writerName": "编程经验随笔", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_123913216.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "28494", "writerRankWeekly": "26208", "writerThumb": "9", "writerVisitNum": "32768", "blog_read_count": "1593", "blog_time": "已于 2022-04-02 15:14:10 修改", "blog_title": "CString头文件怎么用？", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>在非MFC工程中.就包含atlstr.h</p>\n<p>在MFC工程中.就包含afx.h</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>一般我们会使用MFC in ShareDLL的方式</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"526\" src=\"image\\0bc56de964d54f9582af75c6f48ef4db.png\" width=\"767\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>然后需要包含stdafx.h 避免一些编译错误</p>\n<p>stdafx.h的内容如下</p>\n<p>#pragma once</p>\n<p>#ifdef _DEBUG<br/> #define _AFXDLL<br/> #endif<br/> #include &lt;afxwin.h&gt;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>在代码中正常使用 CString 就可以了 不需要ATL::CString去引用，也没有二义性的问题</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>注意：#include \"stdafx.h\"要放在引用的cpp文件的最上面</p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}